Package: lpirfs
Type: Package
Title: Estimate Impulse Response Functions Based on Local Projections by Jordà (2005)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Philipp Adämmer [aut, cre]
Authors@R: c(
            person("Philipp", "Adämmer", 
            email = "adaemmer@hsu-hh.de", 
            role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Philipp Adämmer <adaemmer@hsu-hh.de>
BugReports: https://github.com/adaemmerp/lpirfs/issues
Description: Contains functions to estimate linear and nonlinear impulse 
             responses based on local projections by Jordà (2005) <doi:10.1257/0002828053828518>
             Nonlinear impulse responses are estimated for two regimes which are estimated with 
             a transition function, proposed by Auerbach and Gorodnichenko (2012) <doi:10.1257/pol.4.2.1>.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
NeedsCompilation:	yes
